OL,3,C'Bring on the glitter!' Former
OL,4,CEmmerdale star Charlie Hardwick to
OL,5,Cmake panto return in Sunderland
OL,7,FActor Charlie Hardwick is looking
OL,8,Fforward to her return to pantomime in
OL,9,FSunderland after a six-year break.
OL,11,FThe former Emmerdale star, who played
OL,12,FVal Pollard in the ITV soap for more
OL,13,Fthan a decade, is preparing for her
OL,14,Fpart in a production of Beauty and
OL,15,Fthe Beast at the Sunderland Empire.
OL,17,FFollowing her recent role as Sue Carp
OL,18,Fin Channel 4's comedy drama, Ackley
OL,19,FBridge, Wallsend-born Hardwick said
OL,20,Fshe could not wait to get back to her
OL,21,Froots and tread the boards again.
